Global Network Video Recorder NVR Market Insights
Network Video Recorder NVR Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 8.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.02% from 2024 to 2030.

Network Video Recorder NVR Market Overview
The global Network Video Recorder (NVR) market is expected to reach a market value of approximately USD 13.5 billion by 2025, growing at a CAGR of 15.6% from 2020 to 2025. The rise in demand for advanced surveillance systems across multiple industries such as retail, healthcare, and transportation is propelling this growth. The rapid adoption of IP-based surveillance solutions, as well as the increasing need for security and safety, are key factors driving the market expansion. Additionally, technological advancements in cloud-based services and AI integration further enhance the market's growth trajectory.

